{{etyl|ang}} {{term|stif|stīf|lang=ang}}, from {{etyl|gem-pro|en}} {{recons|stifaz|lang=gem-pro}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} {{recons|stīpos|lang=ine-pro}} (compare {{etyl|la}} {{term|stipare}}, from which English {{term|stevedore}}).

